        </task>
        <task>
            <statement>
                <p>
                    Suppose that the number of downloads have been increasing at a <em>fixed percentage each month</em>. What type of equation is suggested here? Write that equation and use it to estimate the number of downloads in November 2011 (when T = 11).
                </p>
            </statement>
        </task>
        <task>
            <statement>
                <p>
                    Which of these two models do you think is more sensible, and why?
                </p>
